宁。。。。", "like_count": 10, "author_name": "周廷勇", "author_id": "d5aff9679768cfcef9353145b21170ca", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "chen-chen-86-88", "headline": "书法老师  平面设计师  旅游爱好者", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269070442", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我们住的估计是同一家客栈，我记得我当时住4楼，看的风景跟你一毛一样~还有！河边上餐馆的江团鱼超级好吃啊！不知道你有没有尝一尝，至今难忘?", "like_count": 7, "author_name": "陈晨", "author_id": "ecaf9ff2bb57d43c9772208c85f0ebe1", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "yun-yun-126", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269495156", "reply_comment_id": "269070442", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "请问可以问下客栈名字吗？谢谢～", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "云云126", "author_id": "e2c1c75aa078936bb1d0de2a365354c7", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wa-you-yu", "headline": "会计大学生", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269297338", "reply_comment_id": "269070442", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "请问客栈名称是什么？", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "哇 有鱼", "author_id": "0943aa3a11ef30167442f7370747bbac", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "burningred6", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269488654", "reply_comment_id": "269423302", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "贵州天气很好，更何况边边的小镇你看那山那水，不热的！", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "莫非", "author_id": "3836eb684f7cef1182ce4476843030f5", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "littleprince-37", "headline": "经济学在读", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269297800", "reply_comment_id": "269070442", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "嗯，其实对于其他古镇啊，这里的住宿条件已经不错了，而且价格也合理。。对于出行如果吃不好的话也会给旅途留下很不好的印象。这里恰恰食物也好吃，也没像其他景区哄抬物价，还吃不上好的。。。所以给人印象很棒", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "皮皮伟", "author_id": "92a134d598d5ba102709fb43ab3d28f4", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-gu-niang-70-87", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "611645313", "reply_comment_id": "269297338", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "檀庄小荷", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "李姑娘", "author_id": "e20112068d61345d5bbb7e81aa23004e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-gu-niang-70-87", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "611645087", "reply_comment_id": "269070442", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "竟然是一个朋友开的客栈😂😂", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "李姑娘", "author_id": "e20112068d61345d5bbb7e81aa23004e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "goddess-22", "headline": "马上毕业的创业者", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269423302", "reply_comment_id": "269070442", "reply_root_comment_id": "269070442", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "暑假去热不热", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "goddess", "author_id": "bd6dee842ae0676ae6ee10d4f3e12325", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "liu-yang-rui-87", "headline": "感觉自己不知道要做什么了", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269069519", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "269069519", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "突然很想念记忆里的那一座小城，一条浅江一座古桥，桥头三两少年每日嬉戏。突然桥重建了，江也变臟了，故人已成游子，小城慢慢变成了一座大城。我也再也没有见过他们。", "like_count": 7, "author_name": "小笼包子来一笼", "author_id": "a20436f1b44e5177d4c66e7a45dfc723", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269215115", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "刚从镇远回来。房屋是典型的新农村建设风格，统一的徽式白墙黑瓦，砖石结构。河岸两侧全是客栈和商业，现在淡季全架着脚手架统一翻新中。论商业化我觉得不输任何一个成熟古镇，而自身特色却比不上其他古镇。优点是人相对少一点，但据说旺季也是一房难求。<br>优点是确实有些不错的客栈，对于我这个极爱住漂亮客栈的人来说，这点基本满足。但是古镇真心没啥好玩好逛的呢，即便商业也毫无特色，连小吃都只有粉和黄粑。我就住在青龙洞对面的祝圣桥头，夜景不错，当地人好心提醒青龙洞60门票坑爹，除此之外真的没有玩的了。。。幸运的是第二天遇到一位驴友告知他要赶去附近一个叫报京的侗寨去参加三月三讨葱节，于是一起包车过去了还挺有意思的。不然一整天泡在镇里绝对无聊死。真的毫无特色啊。。。如果只是待在客栈里反而好点", "like_count": 6, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "littleprince-37", "headline": "经济学在读", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269299717", "reply_comment_id": "269215115", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是听说最近在整改，改成什么样了我最近也没去看看。青龙洞我也觉得不值票价啊，所以也没写在这里面，有宗教信仰的人可以去看看。其实啊，你可以去小巷里逛逛，问当地人，或者客栈老板，可以从小巷里爬到后山去，后山植被很好，那里可以俯瞰全镇，上次我们还在那遇见了几只松鼠。<br>如果不嫌难走还可以去铁溪看看龙潭。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "皮皮伟", "author_id": "92a134d598d5ba102709fb43ab3d28f4", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269357561", "reply_comment_id": "269253544", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "贵州一圈玩下来最头疼还是交通。我去的都是比较有名的点，交通已然不便。更不用说那些没什么知名度的了。这是一个很矛盾的状态，便利的交通必然伴随成熟的商业化。。。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lu-guo-ing-98", "headline": "前工地狗，现猿。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269253544", "reply_comment_id": "269215115", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "本来就算一个不怎么有特色的“古镇”，基本就是丽江模式。贵州比较有特色的古镇还是有挺多的，只是一般人不大知晓而已，比如像下司以及洪渡镇……", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "路过ing", "author_id": "0f5d90c6220869e7a9c5762ce9fc0ccc", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lu-guo-ing-98", "headline": "前工地狗，现猿。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269579525", "reply_comment_id": "269577704", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我都是看哪个地方名字顺眼……就去哪……除了人文建筑外，自然风光之类的基本不看攻略，除了名气超大的景点……", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "路过ing", "author_id": "0f5d90c6220869e7a9c5762ce9fc0ccc", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269577704", "reply_comment_id": "269539574", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "哈哈哈其实我和朋友坐上凯里到镇远的火车上后，怎么看之后去肇兴都很折腾，于是我说，为什么我们不把镇远跳过直接去肇兴呢？接下来我们差点跳车。。。后来我朋友还一路埋怨我不早提议。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lu-guo-ing-98", "headline": "前工地狗，现猿。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269539574", "reply_comment_id": "269516383", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "所以镇远我直接PASS掉了，荔波的话……实际你可以搭火车到隔壁的地方。虽然也不怎么好玩。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "路过ing", "author_id": "0f5d90c6220869e7a9c5762ce9fc0ccc", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269516383", "reply_comment_id": "269479140", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我也想坐高铁啊，问题是镇远古镇，小七孔茂兰，都没有通高铁啊，小七孔连火车都没通，我们直接放弃了。。。希望未来会更好吧", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "lu-guo-ing-98", "headline": "前工地狗，现猿。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269479140", "reply_comment_id": "269469979", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我的意思是，如果无法自驾不想跟团的话，你可以坐高铁玩哇……贵州主要旅游的就是风光和部分少数民族风情，这俩满贵州都是哇……但这俩也决定了太商业化就没意思了，各种苗寨浓浓的商业气息。我算半个旅游业从业人员，也算资深自助游人员吧……自助游在国内虽然在国内已成主流，但普遍还遗留了一个旅游团的毛病，那就是尽量短的时间去尽量多的地方……这样极容易把自己搞的很疲惫……实际放慢脚步，随心感受，不多的钱即可收获不一样的游玩过程……比如我在高铁某个站呆了一周多。爬爬周边的山，看看古宅，在江上划竹排，风雨桥上钓个鱼，风雨亭里睡个觉，吃吃当地正宗特色，沏壶茶和当地人………所以我的旅行经历好极了，花在路上的时间不过几个小时而已……", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "路过ing", "author_id": "0f5d90c6220869e7a9c5762ce9fc0ccc", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269471225", "reply_comment_id": "269457587", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我拜访过的古镇算多，镇远是最平庸的一个。景色真心一般般，江浙沪皖任何一个统一规划过的新农村新县城新城镇都是那样的。如果只是想无所事事放松心情享受一份宁静安详，就去吧。<br>贵州其他景点都还不错，抛开长距离和不便利的交通，还是值得一览。<br>印象最深的反而是贵州人民的热情，质朴，做为旅游城市居民的高度旅游觉悟。真的很好", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269469979", "reply_comment_id": "269374832", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我是这样来去的。。。但真心折腾。回来朋友问我体验怎样，我的回答是除了睡觉，有一大半时间都在路上。作为一个学旅游也做旅游的人，真心觉得贵州的旅游没有达到集群效应。适合跟团和自驾，不适合像我这样公共交通自由行。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-feng-yan-31", "headline": "不甘做猫奴的铲屎官", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269469152", "reply_comment_id": "269353139", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "旁边的山慢慢爬20分钟就到顶，古镇全景老实说真的不好看。。。对我这种经常走20公里拉练山路的人来说，塞牙缝也不够", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "云风颜", "author_id": "ebcc8803c35c705c7c5eab827f9d69f6", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wu-da-lang-53", "headline": "自家酒厂，杏花村青花瓷，酒厂直发，闲聊：qhc9gd", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "269457587", "reply_comment_id": "269215115", "reply_root_comment_id": "269215115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_a